dev.jeka.core.api.java.project

Class JkJavaProjectTesting

  • java.lang.Object
    • dev.jeka.core.api.java.project.JkJavaProjectTesting

  • public class JkJavaProjectTesting
extends java.lang.Object
    Handles project testing step. This involve both test compilation and run. Users can configure inner phases by chaining runnables. They also can modify JkJavaCompiler, JkJavaCompileSpec for test compilation and JkTestProcessor, JkTestSelection for test run.
